org.libav.avcodec.bridge

Class AVCodec54

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bridj.NativeObject
      • org.bridj.StructObject
        • org.libav.avcodec.bridge.AVCodec54
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativeObjectInterface

    public class AVCodec54
extends StructObject
    Mirror of the native AVCodec struct for the libavcodec v54.x.x and v55.x.x. This class contains only the public API fields, the real AVCodec struct is bigger. For details see the Libav documentation.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
